<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="14300000t" end="47600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">让我们重新回到忍野扇的话题上</font></p>
<p begin="56000000t" end="98500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">然而「她就是她  她也只能是她」的话题</font></p>
<p begin="101000000t" end="134800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">一旦开始  一旦重新  一旦回到</font></p>
<p begin="137300000t" end="163200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这根本性的问题也就立刻迎来了终结</font></p>
<p begin="171900000t" end="209900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如果要在小说中对忍野扇进行一番描述的话</font></p>
<p begin="212400000t" end="238700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">仅仅用一行字就可以完成</font></p>
<p begin="241000000t" end="276000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}忍野扇就是忍野扇</font></p>
<p begin="246600000t" end="271600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">「忍野扇就是忍野扇」</font></p>
<p begin="277500000t" end="292100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">可喜可贺可喜可贺</font></p>
<p begin="294600000t" end="304200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就是如此一行</font></p>
<p begin="314600000t" end="344600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">于是乎  虽然我们之前一直在学习数学</font></p>
<p begin="346300000t" end="368000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过最后还是要来到语文的课堂上</font></p>
<p begin="374600000t" end="387200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">下面便是语文的问题</font></p>
<p begin="392600000t" end="418900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">「对于某问题  请在某某字以内进行说明」</font></p>
<p begin="426400000t" end="452200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">关于忍野扇的问题  正如之前所说</font></p>
<p begin="456000000t" end="494800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如果要以她为中心来出一道问题的话</font></p>
<p begin="487500000t" end="530400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}【问】关于忍野扇  请在四个字以内进行回答</font></p>
<p begin="496400000t" end="528500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那么问题便是「关于忍野扇  请在四个字以内进行回答」</font></p>
<p begin="531900000t" end="556500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">而答案则是「忍野扇」</font></p>
<p begin="540800000t" end="588400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}【答】忍野扇</font></p>
<p begin="559400000t" end="591900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那么我提出的最后一个问题便是如下</font></p>
<p begin="590900000t" end="687700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}【问】阿良良木历究竟有多愚蠢？  请在二十字以内进行回答</font></p>
<p begin="599900000t" end="645690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">「阿良良木历究竟有多愚蠢？  请在二十字以内进行回答」</font></p>
<p begin="647200000t" end="687700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}但文中必须使用一次「忍野扇」</font></p>
<p begin="650300000t" end="687900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">「但文中必须使用一次「忍野扇」」</font></p>
<p begin="1623000000t" end="1639300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="32">{\an8}育与迷失  其一</font></p>
<p begin="1651200000t" end="1672000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">话说你到底弄明白没有啊？阿良良木同学</font></p>
<p begin="1675000000t" end="1713300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">老仓同学为什么会知道阿良良木同学父母的职业？</font></p>
<p begin="1717500000t" end="1745900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯？啊…我已经弄清楚了</font></p>
<p begin="1752100000t" end="1773000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我还找千石确认了一下  肯定没错的</font></p>
<p begin="1777600000t" end="1826400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这种事也用不着这么垂头丧气地来肯定吧</font></p>
<p begin="1831800000t" end="1851000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我当然会垂头丧气了</font></p>
<p begin="1855600000t" end="1882700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不管我多努力回忆都想不起来的事情</font></p>
<p begin="1886000000t" end="1919800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">按照羽川你给我的方法去查了一下立刻就弄清楚了</font></p>
<p begin="1925200000t" end="1957300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">真是的  羽川你真的是什么都知道啊</font></p>
<p begin="1960700000t" end="1992400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我不是什么都知道  我只知道自己知道的事情</font></p>
<p begin="2017800000t" end="2053700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">毕竟我也不知道小扇她究竟都知道些什么</font></p>
<p begin="2076600000t" end="2112100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">没问题吧  她会不会在跟踪我们？</font></p>
<p begin="2127900000t" end="2137900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">跟踪？</font></p>
<p begin="2140800000t" end="2164600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不可能  她又不是什么杀手</font></p>
<p begin="2168200000t" end="2177800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">杀手？</font></p>
<p begin="2184200000t" end="2212200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">跟踪难道不是侦探的行为吗？阿良良木同学</font></p>
<p begin="2277600000t" end="2313100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这时候她要是能跟我们一起来就好了</font></p>
<p begin="2318100000t" end="2343100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">她要真的在后面跟踪的话  我们就不清楚她的行动了</font></p>
<p begin="2349000000t" end="2370700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你是不是有些神经过敏了？</font></p>
<p begin="2373200000t" end="2389000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">可是阿良良木同学</font></p>
<p begin="2390700000t" end="2428600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">虽然她可能没在跟踪我们  可说不定已经在前面等着我们呢</font></p>
<p begin="2429900000t" end="2451100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">毕竟目的地都已经那么明显了</font></p>
<p begin="2452000000t" end="2480300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">要是调查的话还是去那边风险更低一些</font></p>
<p begin="2483300000t" end="2508700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我这不是神经过敏</font></p>
<p begin="2510800000t" end="2529100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如果不是神经过敏的话</font></p>
<p begin="2529100000t" end="2565000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">羽川  那你恐怕就是对小扇的评价过高了</font></p>
<p begin="2575890000t" end="2595000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就算她是忍野先生的外甥女</font></p>
<p begin="2595000000t" end="2621700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">脑子也还算聪明</font></p>
<p begin="2623800000t" end="2658400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">可她归根结底也只是一个小孩子  一个一年级生</font></p>
<p begin="2660500000t" end="2674300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不是还挺可爱的嘛</font></p>
<p begin="2692600000t" end="2730800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">教导她不要让她变成忍野先生那个样子</font></p>
<p begin="2730800000t" end="2757900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这才是我们身为学长和学姐的责任</font></p>
<p begin="2757900000t" end="2780400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">同时也是对忍野先生恩情的一种回报吧</font></p>
<p begin="2786100000t" end="2810300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">报答忍野先生的恩情</font></p>
<p begin="2814800000t" end="2855300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯  你也是用心良着啊  佩服佩服</font></p>
<p begin="2859900000t" end="2917400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我还以为阿良良木同学又迷上了新登场的可爱学妹了呢</font></p>
<p begin="2918700000t" end="2930800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">为什么要说「又」啊？</font></p>
<p begin="2933300000t" end="2975000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">当初神原同学出现的时候  阿良良木同学不就是和现在一样吗？</font></p>
<p begin="2978800000t" end="3015000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如果你真的是这么考虑的话  那你还是不要这样了</font></p>
<p begin="3015000000t" end="3036300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">现在班上出现这么多麻烦事</font></p>
<p begin="3039700000t" end="3071400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">可没时间让你围着学妹转圈还引来一系列误会了</font></p>
<p begin="3075900000t" end="3090100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">属下铭记在心</font></p>
<p begin="3094300000t" end="3103100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那就好</font></p>
<p begin="3116400000t" end="3130600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我先确认一下</font></p>
<p begin="3130600000t" end="3165400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">阿良良木同学在陪小扇一起进行实地考察之前</font></p>
<p begin="3165400000t" end="3201300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">一直都没记起老仓同学初中时候的事情吗？</font></p>
<p begin="3207300000t" end="3218800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不  不是这样不是这样</font></p>
<p begin="3218800000t" end="3225500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">说反了说反了</font></p>
<p begin="3233600000t" end="3265700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">是小扇陪我一起去实地考察的</font></p>
<p begin="3269900000t" end="3303700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">小扇她基本上只是跟着我而已</font></p>
<p begin="3308300000t" end="3336600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">只是在帮助我找回关于老仓的记忆而已</font></p>
<p begin="3340000000t" end="3355000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯…嗯？</font></p>
<p begin="3359600000t" end="3411300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">总觉得你没听懂我说什么  是我表达得不够清楚吗？</font></p>
<p begin="3419200000t" end="3455900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">从我的角度来看  我可从没见过这么危险的孩子</font></p>
<p begin="3458000000t" end="3466700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">危险？</font></p>
<p begin="3471300000t" end="3484300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你是指老仓吗？</font></p>
<p begin="3495500000t" end="3511400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你看  根本谈不到一起去</font></p>
<p begin="3520100000t" end="3553500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就好像阿良良木同学在故意偷换论题一样</font></p>
<p begin="3595200000t" end="3646100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">算了  也罢  你现在一定是没法谈这些吧</font></p>
<p begin="3661900000t" end="3727000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">羽川  如果你认为小扇对老仓抱有某种恶意的话那就错了</font></p>
<p begin="3730800000t" end="3760800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">毕竟小扇她从来就没见过老仓</font></p>
<p begin="3764500000t" end="3793700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我不是在担心这些  阿良良木同学</font></p>
<p begin="3795800000t" end="3850900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我一丁点也没有担心过小扇会盯上老仓</font></p>
<p begin="3854200000t" end="3873800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我担心的是…</font></p>
<p begin="3875500000t" end="3883000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">是什么？</font></p>
<p begin="3886300000t" end="3908400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我担心的是阿良良木同学你</font></p>
<p begin="3912600000t" end="3946800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">说不定是你被一些莫名其妙的东西盯上了</font></p>
<p begin="3955600000t" end="3971800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">莫名其妙的东西？</font></p>
<p begin="3973900000t" end="4001400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">或许应该说是一种不太妙的东西</font></p>
<p begin="4006000000t" end="4041500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">说实话  连我也没有能保护好你的自信</font></p>
<p begin="4045700000t" end="4053200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">保护我？</font></p>
<p begin="4054800000t" end="4092400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">虽然阿良良木同学把春假时候的事情称作「地狱」</font></p>
<p begin="4097400000t" end="4128200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">但说不定接下来才是阿良良木同学真正受难的时候</font></p>
<p begin="4154500000t" end="4211700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我们  羽川班长以及阿良良木副班长已经来到了目的地</font></p>
<p begin="4255500000t" end="4282600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">也就是老仓育现在的住处</font></p>
<p begin="4308000000t" end="4332200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">老仓育前班长</font></p>
<p begin="4334300000t" end="4366000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">从那第二天开始再一次休学在家</font></p>
<p begin="4387900000t" end="4419600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">或许是敏感地感觉到周围的气氛不妙</font></p>
<p begin="4422900000t" end="4455900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">战场原从那一天开始也没有来上学</font></p>
<p begin="4464800000t" end="4483200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">于是乎  阿良良木同学</font></p>
<p begin="4484800000t" end="4513200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">今天放学以后我们一起去看望她们一下吧</font></p>
<p begin="4519500000t" end="4539500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">看望战场原同学还有老仓同学</font></p>
<p begin="4555800000t" end="4590400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">毕竟时间有限  我们还是分头行动比较好</font></p>
<p begin="4596600000t" end="4606200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">战场原同学还有老仓同学</font></p>
<p begin="4606200000t" end="4616900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">战场原同学还有老仓同学</font></p>
<p begin="4620400000t" end="4645000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">阿良良木同学想要去看望谁啊？</font></p>
<p begin="4658400000t" end="4677100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这就让阿良良木同学来选好了</font></p>
<p begin="4716700000t" end="4729300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">是去探望恋人</font></p>
<p begin="4734300000t" end="4746800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">还是去探望仇敌</font></p>
<p begin="4755100000t" end="4776800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这的确是一个极其简单的选择</font></p>
<p begin="4782600000t" end="4806000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">然而我选择的却是后者</font></p>
<p begin="4824400000t" end="4871900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你问明明是分头行动为什么最终又和羽川同学会合了？</font></p>
<p begin="4874200000t" end="4896700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}她的受难</font></p>
<p begin="4877300000t" end="4894000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">事情的经过是这样的</font></p>
<p begin="4908200000t" end="4938200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哎？这不是阿良良木学长吗？</font></p>
<p begin="4955300000t" end="4965300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">小扇</font></p>
<p begin="4976600000t" end="4993700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">小扇  你这是要回家吗？</font></p>
<p begin="4997900000t" end="5007000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">回家？</font></p>
<p begin="5011200000t" end="5060400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这个…不是  你到底在说什么啊阿良良木学长</font></p>
<p begin="5062100000t" end="5093800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我们不是说好了在这儿见面的吗？</font></p>
<p begin="5103800000t" end="5150490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不是说好了下午3点42分的时候在校门口见面的吗？</font></p>
<p begin="5157200000t" end="5172600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">真不愧是阿良良木学长</font></p>
<p begin="5174290000t" end="5198090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">分秒不差  完全正确</font></p>
<p begin="5201000000t" end="5224290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">您在这些地方还真是认真啊</font></p>
<p begin="5229800000t" end="5241900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你这个愚蠢的家伙</font></p>
<p begin="5269400000t" end="5285200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哇  真开心</font></p>
<p begin="5290200000t" end="5335700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">阿良良木学长接下来居然要带我去吃不旋转的寿司呢</font></p>
<p begin="5336900000t" end="5356600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我什么时候说过这种话了！</font></p>
<p begin="5358600000t" end="5390800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">当然说过了  为了庆祝我转学嘛</font></p>
<p begin="5394900000t" end="5420800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">庆祝个转学就吃不旋转的寿司</font></p>
<p begin="5424500000t" end="5454600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那这转到我们学校的到底是谁家的大人物啊？</font></p>
<p begin="5500900000t" end="5515000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">抱歉  小扇</font></p>
<p begin="5518800000t" end="5548400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">很遗憾  我不能履行和你的约定</font></p>
<p begin="5551700000t" end="5580100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哎呀  这么帅气的台词是什么意思？</font></p>
<p begin="5583000000t" end="5609700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">明明自己打破了约定还说这么帅气的台词</font></p>
<p begin="5611400000t" end="5630600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">接下来是不是要说没带钱了？</font></p>
<p begin="5634300000t" end="5676000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我接下来要去一趟老仓家  小扇</font></p>
<p begin="5678100000t" end="5710700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哦  你又要去那间废屋啊</font></p>
<p begin="5714800000t" end="5740700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不  不是那间废屋  是她现在的住处</font></p>
<p begin="5740500000t" end="5748000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}嗯</font></p>
<p begin="5757600000t" end="5772600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}糟了，</font></p>
<p begin="5759700000t" end="5772600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}我又在扇的面前</font></p>
<p begin="5762200000t" end="5772600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}一个字不漏地全都说出来了</font></p>
<p begin="5862100000t" end="5873700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你干嘛呀！</font></p>
<p begin="5876700000t" end="5903800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不  我只是想把你嘴上的拉链拉开而已</font></p>
<p begin="5909200000t" end="5940900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">其实也不是拉链  应该是像魔术胶带一样的东西</font></p>
<p begin="5944600000t" end="5974300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">再跟我说一说嘛  求求您了</font></p>
<p begin="5979700000t" end="5990900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">发生了什么事情？</font></p>
<p begin="5995500000t" end="6034300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">您这是准备以惊人的速度攻略老仓学姐吗？</font></p>
<p begin="6037200000t" end="6054300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">真是日新月异啊</font></p>
<p begin="6057300000t" end="6086000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">快把至今为止的经过全都向我汇报一下</font></p>
<p begin="6088500000t" end="6096500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">愚蠢的家伙</font></p>
<p begin="6101000000t" end="6127300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不  才不是什么攻略呢</font></p>
<p begin="6131100000t" end="6166900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这也不是双方约好的访问  而是我单方面去打扰她才对</font></p>
<p begin="6173200000t" end="6199900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">从昨天开始  她又不来上学了</font></p>
<p begin="6204900000t" end="6231200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">其实前天那样也不算是来了</font></p>
<p begin="6232600000t" end="6243900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}我  无可奈何地开始说明</font></p>
<p begin="6252900000t" end="6263300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就是这么一回事</font></p>
<p begin="6267500000t" end="6283300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">原来就是这么一回事啊</font></p>
<p begin="6285800000t" end="6312100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">虽然我也没有详细问过</font></p>
<p begin="6315400000t" end="6350000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">她现在似乎已经离开父母生活了</font></p>
<p begin="6353000000t" end="6370500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">离开父母？</font></p>
<p begin="6372600000t" end="6415900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">也就是说住在亲戚家咯</font></p>
<p begin="6418000000t" end="6438500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不  据说好像是一个人生活</font></p>
<p begin="6440600000t" end="6472200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哎？这也挺有意思的</font></p>
<p begin="6487300000t" end="6511900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">所以  或许正像小扇你之前说的那样</font></p>
<p begin="6514800000t" end="6548200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">她父母一定是在五年前就已经离婚或者怎么样了</font></p>
<p begin="6553600000t" end="6571100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">应该说是家庭破裂吧</font></p>
<p begin="6575300000t" end="6598600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">然后两年前  她又回到了这里</font></p>
<p begin="6603200000t" end="6614100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">原来如此</font></p>
<p begin="6618200000t" end="6637800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我随口乱说的推理居然说中了</font></p>
<p begin="6649900000t" end="6667400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过  阿良良木学长</font></p>
<p begin="6669100000t" end="6687000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">愚蠢的阿良良木学长</font></p>
<p begin="6688700000t" end="6751700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">也就是说阿良良木学长接下来要去拜访一名独自生活的女孩子咯</font></p>
<p begin="6776300000t" end="6789200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这可不太妙</font></p>
<p begin="6789200000t" end="6808800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不太妙吗？</font></p>
<p begin="6813000000t" end="6831800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不妙  相当不妙</font></p>
<p begin="6834700000t" end="6856400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">根本不是绅士应该有的行为</font></p>
<p begin="6859300000t" end="6894800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">由男性一个人去拜访独自生活的单身女性</font></p>
<p begin="6894800000t" end="6921900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那他们之间的关系肯定会被周围人所怀疑的</font></p>
<p begin="6926000000t" end="6959000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">毕竟您也是有女朋友的人</font></p>
<p begin="6999400000t" end="7020700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">看来您的决心还是蛮坚定的嘛</font></p>
<p begin="7024900000t" end="7060300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我真是白期待不回转的寿司了</font></p>
<p begin="7070800000t" end="7082900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那回头见  小扇</font></p>
<p begin="7082900000t" end="7123300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">啊  对了  我想到一个好主意  阿良良木学长</font></p>
<p begin="7133700000t" end="7170900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">您就带着不中用的我一起去家访好了</font></p>
<p begin="7172100000t" end="7186300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哎？小扇也一起去？</font></p>
<p begin="7190500000t" end="7205500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那倒是件好事</font></p>
<p begin="7220300000t" end="7232800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}嗯？真的是件好事吗？</font></p>
<p begin="7237600000t" end="7263000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">也就是说  只要不是你一个人去就可以了</font></p>
<p begin="7265500000t" end="7291800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">更何况我还是个女孩子</font></p>
<p begin="7294300000t" end="7333500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我陪你一起的话  老仓学姐的情绪也会变得缓和一些吧</font></p>
<p begin="7336900000t" end="7372300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就算是面对女孩子  她恐怕也不会变得缓和吧</font></p>
<p begin="7402300000t" end="7412600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}不知道面对学妹会不会稍微缓和一些</font></p>
<p begin="7419000000t" end="7453200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">正如您知道的  我很擅长倾听</font></p>
<p begin="7457000000t" end="7499100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">说不定可以从老仓学姐哪里问出不少事情呢</font></p>
<p begin="7504100000t" end="7515000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">问出不少事情？</font></p>
<p begin="7528300000t" end="7594200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">虽然阿良良木学长回想起了之前的班会还有初一暑假的事情</font></p>
<p begin="7594200000t" end="7618000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">也想起了老仓学姐的过去</font></p>
<p begin="7621300000t" end="7660100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">但是您和现在的她还从来没能好好地聊过不是吗？</font></p>
<p begin="7665900000t" end="7702600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">为了防止引起什么口角  我会在我们之间做一个缓冲</font></p>
<p begin="7731400000t" end="7763100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">什么嘛  毕竟都已经上了这条船</font></p>
<p begin="7769400000t" end="7789400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">您就让我出这份力吧</font></p>
<p begin="7863600000t" end="7887800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那么  小扇  接下来就拜托你了</font></p>
<p begin="7893300000t" end="7910400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">好的  那就拜托我吧</font></p>
<p begin="7919500000t" end="7932500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不能拜托她！</font></p>
<p begin="8031700000t" end="8056300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你可干万不能拜托她  阿良良木同学</font></p>
<p begin="8067600000t" end="8075900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">羽川…</font></p>
<p begin="8095100000t" end="8106000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这怎么能行</font></p>
<p begin="8109700000t" end="8145200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你想  咱们班里的事情怎么能把学妹也牵连进来呢</font></p>
<p begin="8155000000t" end="8165000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}啊。是这个意思？是怎么回事？</font></p>
<p begin="8165000000t" end="8172100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}内部的事情让外面的人插手的确不太好</font></p>
<p begin="8177700000t" end="8184000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">小扇</font></p>
<p begin="8184000000t" end="8233200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不不不不  您不用这么客气的  阿良良木学长</font></p>
<p begin="8239000000t" end="8258600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">您这样说会让我很伤心的</font></p>
<p begin="8269900000t" end="8293700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">您不用在意我的</font></p>
<p begin="8294900000t" end="8308300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我一点也不在意的</font></p>
<p begin="8311200000t" end="8326200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">所以您也不用在意我的</font></p>
<p begin="8328700000t" end="8369600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不如说到了这时候你们还说这些见外的话实在让我有些受打击</font></p>
<p begin="8376700000t" end="8387900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">晴天霹雳啊</font></p>
<p begin="8427500000t" end="8458000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我和阿良良木学长又不是一般的关系</font></p>
<p begin="8475500000t" end="8504700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你和阿良良木同学到底是什么关系？</font></p>
<p begin="8530600000t" end="8572700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你和阿良良木同学不是大前天才认识的吗？</font></p>
<p begin="8585600000t" end="8601900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯  没错</font></p>
<p begin="8605200000t" end="8649400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">可是人和人之间的关系又不是非要用时间来衡量</font></p>
<p begin="8657300000t" end="8714100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我可是在很短的时间里就和阿良良木学长意气相投了</font></p>
<p begin="8717600000t" end="8737200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">一起被关在神秘的教室当中</font></p>
<p begin="8742900000t" end="8759500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">一起去废屋进行冒险</font></p>
<p begin="8766200000t" end="8802500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">一起经历了许多常人不会经历的事情</font></p>
<p begin="8808300000t" end="8827100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">是吧  阿良良木学长</font></p>
<p begin="8830000000t" end="8850900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯  那当然</font></p>
<p begin="8860500000t" end="8895900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">啊  嗯  这些事我都听说了</font></p>
<p begin="8899700000t" end="8947600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">阿良良木同学  我这个重要的朋友似乎也受到你不少照顾</font></p>
<p begin="9001000000t" end="9024400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我一定要谢谢你才行</font></p>
<p begin="9034400000t" end="9069800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过要是换成我  一定会做得比你还要好就是了</font></p>
<p begin="9102000000t" end="9118200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哎？是嘛</font></p>
<p begin="9124100000t" end="9138700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哎  可能是吧</font></p>
<p begin="9143300000t" end="9179500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">要是换成羽川学姐的话一定会做得比我更好吧</font></p>
<p begin="9182900000t" end="9205000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">毕竟你是个天才嘛</font></p>
<p begin="9208300000t" end="9241300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这些我都从舅舅那里听说了</font></p>
<p begin="9244600000t" end="9280100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">舅舅？你是指忍野先生吗？</font></p>
<p begin="9294700000t" end="9310100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">没错  因为我是他的外甥女</font></p>
<p begin="9328400000t" end="9368500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过您的天才如果没处发挥的话也就没什么意义了</font></p>
<p begin="9374700000t" end="9415200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">事实上  当时在阿良良木学长身边的人是我</font></p>
<p begin="9428100000t" end="9457700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">连舅舅都忌惮你的天才头脑</font></p>
<p begin="9463200000t" end="9514000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过从这件事来看  似乎也没有他说的那么厉害嘛</font></p>
<p begin="9525700000t" end="9550300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如果换成我听说的那个羽川翼</font></p>
<p begin="9552000000t" end="9597000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">在阿良良木学长身处危机的时候  是不可能不在他的身边的</font></p>
<p begin="9607500000t" end="9649600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如果说您能做得比我好  那指的也应该是全盛期时候的您吧</font></p>
<p begin="9652500000t" end="9693800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">喂喂  小扇  话可不能这么说</font></p>
<p begin="9697100000t" end="9719200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">有些话可以说  有些话不能说</font></p>
<p begin="9723000000t" end="9746800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">关于羽川你又知道些什么？</font></p>
<p begin="9756400000t" end="9775500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我什么都不知道</font></p>
<p begin="9786000000t" end="9814800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">是你自己知道  阿良良木学长</font></p>
<p begin="9826900000t" end="9877700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">羽川学姐的过去  现在  和未来</font></p>
<p begin="9904400000t" end="9956600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">没错  这些话的确不应该由我来说</font></p>
<p begin="9964900000t" end="10012900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">算了  羽川学姐  我还不至于蠢到和你为敌</font></p>
<p begin="10018300000t" end="10036600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我可不想惹您不开心</font></p>
<p begin="10036600000t" end="10069200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">从而导致我最喜欢的阿良良木学长讨厌我</font></p>
<p begin="10074200000t" end="10092900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我们两个就井水不犯河水吧</font></p>
<p begin="10098800000t" end="10108000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">打扰了</font></p>
<p begin="10117600000t" end="10169300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">您请您请  您不是要去看望战场原学姐吗？</font></p>
<p begin="10172600000t" end="10215600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">她家离这里比较远  我劝您还是早点出发比较好</font></p>
<p begin="10221800000t" end="10230600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">比较远？</font></p>
<p begin="10245200000t" end="10258490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">请您放心</font></p>
<p begin="10261900000t" end="10327800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如果您不想看到重要的朋友阿良良木学长低头求助于学妹的样子</font></p>
<p begin="10329400000t" end="10346500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我自然也不会采取这样的方式</font></p>
<p begin="10353190000t" end="10382800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">因为这本来就是我主动提出来的请求</font></p>
<p begin="10387000000t" end="10434500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">是我擅自要求和阿良良木同学同行的</font></p>
<p begin="10438690000t" end="10451600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就像背后灵一样</font></p>
<p begin="10457900000t" end="10476190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这样就最问题了吧</font></p>
<p begin="10480400000t" end="10525500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就像推理小说里经常出现的那些不请自来的助手一样</font></p>
<p begin="10528000000t" end="10538400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不请自来的助手？</font></p>
<p begin="10547200000t" end="10585500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">毕竟我也不能丢下遇到麻烦的阿良良木学长不管</font></p>
<p begin="10592600000t" end="10629700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">是我主动要求帮助阿良良木学长的</font></p>
<p begin="10636000000t" end="10660600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">人只能自己救自己</font></p>
<p begin="10668100000t" end="10680600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">难道不是这样的吗？</font></p>
<p begin="10685200000t" end="10705200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那只是我舅舅的立场</font></p>
<p begin="10706900000t" end="10738200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我的立场应该是更像仙鹤报恩那样吧</font></p>
<p begin="10741900000t" end="10755700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">仙鹤报恩？</font></p>
<p begin="10770300000t" end="10792800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">也可以说是笠地藏那样</font></p>
<p begin="10796200000t" end="10825300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">简单说就是「滴水之恩当以涌泉相报」</font></p>
<p begin="10830800000t" end="10854500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">还是让人觉得报得太过那种</font></p>
<p begin="10859500000t" end="10910000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">因为阿良良木学长对刚转学过来的我非常友好</font></p>
<p begin="10913400000t" end="10951700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">于是对于这份恩情  我自然会以身相报</font></p>
<p begin="10995500000t" end="11016800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">阿良良木同学  计划有变</font></p>
<p begin="11024700000t" end="11064300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我也去老仓同学家  和阿良良木同学一起</font></p>
<p begin="11098500000t" end="11131500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这样一来你就没什么意见了吧  小扇</font></p>
<p begin="11133600000t" end="11195300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如果说让阿良良木同学一个男生去老仓同学家有些不太合适</font></p>
<p begin="11196600000t" end="11232000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那么如果有我陪同就没有任何问题了吧</font></p>
<p begin="11234900000t" end="11249100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你也就没有任何借口了</font></p>
<p begin="11265000000t" end="11276600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我说的没错吧</font></p>
<p begin="11279600000t" end="11305400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">先不管有没有问题</font></p>
<p begin="11307900000t" end="11366700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">您不是还要去战场原学姐家吗？羽川学姐</font></p>
<p begin="11373400000t" end="11390900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">真想不到</font></p>
<p begin="11393000000t" end="11417600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">居然把好朋友放在最后</font></p>
<p begin="11421400000t" end="11461400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我本来就打算和战场原同学好好长谈一次</font></p>
<p begin="11464300000t" end="11486400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">所以今晚就准备住在她家</font></p>
<p begin="11490600000t" end="11531100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">在战场原家开一场久违的睡衣派对</font></p>
<p begin="11530800000t" end="11538400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}睡衣派对？</font></p>
<p begin="11542700000t" end="11554800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这样就没问题了吧</font></p>
<p begin="11557700000t" end="11595300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">因为我可以做得比你更好</font></p>
<p begin="11598200000t" end="11633700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这世上可不是什么事都做得好就可以的</font></p>
<p begin="11637800000t" end="11676200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">做得太好同样会失去平衡</font></p>
<p begin="11682000000t" end="11705000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">因为那样就不满足中庸的条件了</font></p>
<p begin="11709600000t" end="11740000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">您也应该明白这个道理吧</font></p>
<p begin="11747100000t" end="11772500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">先不说好与不好的问题</font></p>
<p begin="11775500000t" end="11810100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">因为最终做决定的并不是我  而是阿良良木学长</font></p>
<p begin="11838000000t" end="11867600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">是和我一起去  还是和羽川学姐一起去</font></p>
<p begin="11871800000t" end="11901800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这要由阿良良木学长自己做决定</font></p>
<p begin="11906000000t" end="11921900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">决策权就交到你手里了</font></p>
<p begin="11925200000t" end="11981100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我和羽川学姐都会全面服从您的决定  对吧</font></p>
<p begin="11983600000t" end="12007800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">没错  就让阿良良木同学来做决定吧</font></p>
<p begin="12012400000t" end="12035300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这种事毕竟不能强求</font></p>
<p begin="12081600000t" end="12114100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">话说阿良良木学长  这可不行啊</font></p>
<p begin="12117100000t" end="12174200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">怎么能因为自己个人的事情来麻烦羽川学姐这个重要的恩人呢</font></p>
<p begin="12178400000t" end="12216700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">说起内部和外部  毕竟羽川学姐也是外人</font></p>
<p begin="12221300000t" end="12271400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">阿良良木学长也不想给羽川学姐添麻烦吧</font></p>
<p begin="12277800000t" end="12287900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}正是这样</font></p>
<p begin="12287900000t" end="12297000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}这孩子说的话真是再正确不过了</font></p>
<p begin="12300200000t" end="12319300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我们做个约定吧  阿良良木学长</font></p>
<p begin="12322700000t" end="12341000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如果您和我一起去的话</font></p>
<p begin="12343900000t" end="12360200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不论面对什么样的谜题</font></p>
<p begin="12361500000t" end="12391900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我都会给您提示一个解决办法的</font></p>
<p begin="12393400000t" end="12403400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}好吧，既然都说到这个份儿上了</font></p>
<p begin="12437400000t" end="12457400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我们也做个约定吧  阿良良木同学</font></p>
<p begin="12465700000t" end="12482800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如果你和我一起去的话</font></p>
<p begin="12508300000t" end="12527900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我就让你摸我的胸</font></p>
<p begin="12591300000t" end="12614600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就是这里的444号房间吗？</font></p>
<p begin="12619200000t" end="12654300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">看来这个管理公司也不怎么上心嘛</font></p>
<p begin="12657200000t" end="12683900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">与其说是公寓  不如说是公共住宅</font></p>
<p begin="12687600000t" end="12724300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">老仓同学应该是在靠某些社会补助生活吧</font></p>
<p begin="12726800000t" end="12732700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">补助？</font></p>
<p begin="12735600000t" end="12748900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯  公共方面的</font></p>
<p begin="12751600000t" end="12781500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">应该是通过那些机构介绍到的这里的房子吧</font></p>
<p begin="12789400000t" end="12830700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">关于我新得知的关于老仓和我小学时代的回忆</font></p>
<p begin="12837400000t" end="12864100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">可既然连千石都知道的话</font></p>
<p begin="12865700000t" end="12885300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那我为什么就忘得一干二净呢</font></p>
<p begin="12891600000t" end="12919500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不  我一定不是忘记了</font></p>
<p begin="12935400000t" end="12969600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这么一想  我还真是个冷漠的家伙</font></p>
<p begin="12971700000t" end="13003800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">说起来  我之前连千石的事情都已经忘记了</font></p>
<p begin="13005400000t" end="13027100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">刚开始见面的时候一点也没认出来</font></p>
<p begin="13053400000t" end="13081800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我觉得这也是没办法的事情</font></p>
<p begin="13110500000t" end="13132200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不管是千石妹妹还是老仓同学</font></p>
<p begin="13133500000t" end="13167300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你们之间都没有什么令你印象深刻的事情吧</font></p>
<p begin="13181000000t" end="13206500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那阿良良木同学  你稍微等一下</font></p>
<p begin="13208600000t" end="13234800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯？站在楼梯这儿等吗？为什么？</font></p>
<p begin="13239800000t" end="13265300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">因为老仓同学她不是一个人住吗？</font></p>
<p begin="13267000000t" end="13301600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">要是我们按了门铃之后  她穿着睡衣就跑出来</font></p>
<p begin="13304900000t" end="13342900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这要是被阿良良木同学看到了  她恐怕会很难为情的</font></p>
<p begin="13403300000t" end="13412500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">谁？</font></p>
<p begin="13435900000t" end="13451100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">她们到底在吵些什么？</font></p>
<p begin="13451100000t" end="13482400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">可是那剑拔弩张的气势…</font></p>
<p begin="13493000000t" end="13525500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">或许很多人会误会</font></p>
<p begin="13527600000t" end="13587300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">其实我并不是因为羽川的胸部才放弃小扇而选她做搭档的</font></p>
<p begin="13593900000t" end="13641900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我只是因为羽川居然说出这种话而感到了某种不寻常的气氛</font></p>
<p begin="13643600000t" end="13678200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">才在二选一里面选择了她作为我的搭档</font></p>
<p begin="13691100000t" end="13710700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">真有些对不起小扇</font></p>
<p begin="13717000000t" end="13731600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">今后一定要好好补偿她一下</font></p>
<p begin="13734900000t" end="13762400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我以后要做一个能全方面考虑问题的人</font></p>
<p begin="13770400000t" end="13799600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">也是  先不说什么不回转的寿司</font></p>
<p begin="13799600000t" end="13825000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">要不下次先带她去吃一次会回转的寿司</font></p>
<p begin="13836300000t" end="13863800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">阿良良木同学  你可以出来了</font></p>
<p begin="13868000000t" end="13888400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你说可以出来…可是…</font></p>
<p begin="13888400000t" end="13912600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我是说可以进去了  可以进屋了</font></p>
<p begin="13915500000t" end="13966000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过我把话先说清楚  她穿的的确是睡衣</font></p>
<p begin="13976400000t" end="14016900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哎？你刚才不正是要回避这种情形吗？</font></p>
<p begin="14021900000t" end="14064000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">她说不想因为阿良良木来了就刻意去换衣服</font></p>
<p begin="14072300000t" end="14091500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我已经很努力地想要说服她</font></p>
<p begin="14094000000t" end="14127800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">可我越说她就越顽固  说什么也不肯换</font></p>
<p begin="14127800000t" end="14156600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle376"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">还说什么如果我再说下去她就裸体待客</font></p>
<p begin="14162400000t" end="14172900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle377"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我实在是没辙了</font></p>
<p begin="14179100000t" end="14243800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle378"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">放心吧  我又不是那种看了女孩子穿着睡衣就感到兴奋的人</font></p>
<p begin="14245400000t" end="14253800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle379"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这可难说</font></p>
<p begin="14259200000t" end="14288000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle380"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">对我的胸部不安好心的家伙还有脸说这些？</font></p>
<p begin="14300300000t" end="14312800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle381"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}结果她本人是最不理解我一番苦心的。</font></p>
<p begin="14316300000t" end="14354700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle382"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">既然门已经打开  我也没有理由不踏进去</font></p>
<p begin="14359300000t" end="14387700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle383"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就算这是如同宣战布告一般打开的城门</font></p>
<p begin="14391400000t" end="14411800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle384"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我也必须前去迎战</font></p>
<p begin="14418100000t" end="14428500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle385"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这就是我</font></p>
<p begin="14432300000t" end="14475200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle386"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">身为老仓育儿时伙伴的责任</font></p>
<p begin="14522600000t" end="14581800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle387"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">耳畔又传来你的笑声</font></p>
<p begin="14522600000t" end="14581800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle388"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}横で君の笑い声が聞こえる</font></p>
<p begin="14581800000t" end="14642700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle389"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">那本应该永远伴我身边的声音</font></p>
<p begin="14581800000t" end="14642700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle390"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}ずっと隣にいたはずの声</font></p>
<p begin="14764100000t" end="14846700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle391"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">在教室窗子上呼气的水雾中写下的名字</font></p>
<p begin="14764100000t" end="14846700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle392"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}教室の窓に息を吐いて描いた名前</font></p>
<p begin="14846700000t" end="14877100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle393"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">我慌忙地用袖子将它檫去</font></p>
<p begin="14846700000t" end="14877100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle394"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}もぅ慌てて袖で消した</font></p>
<p begin="14877100000t" end="14944300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle395"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">那是因为走廊中传来了你的声音</font></p>
<p begin="14877100000t" end="14944300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle396"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}廊下から君の声がしたから</font></p>
<p begin="14944300000t" end="15016400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle397"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">我假装毫不在意  早早地回了家</font></p>
<p begin="14944300000t" end="15016400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle398"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}心誤魔化すように早足で帰った</font></p>
<p begin="15016400000t" end="15099800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle399"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">不知从什么时候起我无法和你说话</font></p>
<p begin="15016400000t" end="15099800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle400"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}何時からか私は君と話せなくなった</font></p>
<p begin="15100700000t" end="15159900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle401"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">耳畔又传来你的笑声</font></p>
<p begin="15100700000t" end="15159900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle402"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}横で君の笑い声が聞こえる</font></p>
<p begin="15160300000t" end="15216600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle403"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">那本应该永远伴我身边的声音</font></p>
<p begin="15160300000t" end="15216600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle404"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}ずっと隣にいたはずの声</font></p>
<p begin="15216600000t" end="15272900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle405"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">无须说出任何话语就可以注意到自己的人比什么都重要</font></p>
<p begin="15216600000t" end="15272900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle406"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}何も言わなくたって すぐ気付いてくれた人</font></p>
<p begin="15272900000t" end="15342600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle407"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">即时此刻注意到这一点  然而我们已经无法再面对</font></p>
<p begin="15272900000t" end="15342600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle408"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}何より大切と気付いても もう目も合わない</font></p>
